E4Plus1.uk.description: Ticking Clocks: Peralta and the squad track down a hacker who infiltrates the precinct's servers, compromising protected information on undercover agents. (S6 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer Is Where the Art Isn't: Homer learns to love a Miro painting. Then it's stolen - and he gets the blame. (S29 Ep12/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: King Leer: Moe inherits a mattress business from his father, then lands in an all-out war with his siblings. (S29 Ep16/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: At another emotionally charged Commitment Ceremony, one couple affirm their love, a bride's behaviour is called out and there's solo sofa surfing... again. (S10 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: More clips from Rude Tube's naughty little sister, including a zombie prank, cats singing the Star Wars theme, a hilarious pee prank and an escaped honey badger.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tesla Recoil: Leonard and Howard learn that Sheldon went to work with the military behind their backs. Bernadette thinks Ruchi's trying to steal her job. (S11 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Mook, the Chef, the Wife and Her Homer: Homer becomes the boss of Fat Tony's mob when Tony's son decides to become a chef rather than go into the family business. (S18 Ep1/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Jazzy and the Pussycats: Bart takes up playing the drums, upstages Lisa and joins a top jazz band. So Lisa turns her back on music and starts rescuing animals instead. (S18 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: After Clare's deadly scheme, a resident's hunt for answers takes them to Brookside Close, where they're met by someone who's not afraid to speak her mind: Sheila Grant.

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Hollyoaks Unwrapped
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Alex Fletcher, Tisha Merry, Gemma Bissix, Charlie Wernham and Gary Lucy join Kieron Richardson for a deep dive into the world of Hollyoaks as it celebrates 30 years. (Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's rural retreat time, and a welcome romantic break for some. But rumours about a bride's behaviour spiral, and another bride learns a heartbreaking truth. (S10 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics have been watching The Masked Singer, Trigger Point, Pam & Tommy, First Dates: Valentine's, Mary Beard's Forgotten Art, and Dragons' Den. (S19 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Hollyoaks Later
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new: Hollyoaks Later collides with Brookside as residents escape the Close for Liverpool's luxury suburbs, where old secrets ignite new betrayals when a party turns deadly.
